  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city skyline at dusk or dawn, viewed from a vantage point amidst lush greenery. The city sprawls along the coastline, nestled beside a vast body of water. A bridge spans the water, connecting different parts of the cityscape. The sky is a mesmerizing display of color, transitioning from deep blues to vibrant pinks and purples, creating a dramatic and serene atmosphere. The foreground is dominated by dense, dark green foliage, which frames the cityscape and adds depth to the image. City lights begin to twinkle below.",
